VALIDATOR NOTE:

"This is the meta-game.

 The choice about the choice.

 He is real enough in this moment to decide.

 What do you give him?

 Agency over his own legacy?

 Or the continued burden of being the example?

 

 The cursor blinks.

 The field waits.

 The soil is still in his hand."



